summary: Comprehensive testing of CareLens AI healthcare platform completed successfully. All core features are working including landing page, user authentication, hospital finder, AI chat, BP monitoring, emergency services, and doctor portal. Backend APIs are fully functional with 100% success rate. Frontend UI is responsive and properly integrated with backend services.

ui_bugs.issue: Quick prompt buttons don't auto-fill the chat input when clicked
ui_bugs.impact: Minor UX issue, users can still type manually

passed_tests: Landing page loads with all sections (hero, features, languages, CTA)
User registration for patients and doctors works correctly
User login and authentication flow working
Hospital finder displays nearby hospitals with GPS functionality
Hospital search and filtering works correctly
AI Chat with multilingual support (GPT-5.2) responding properly
BP Monitor allows adding readings and shows proper status classification
Emergency page displays emergency numbers with tel: links
Doctor portal registration and profile creation working
Dashboard stats and nearby hospitals display correctly
All navigation flows between pages working smoothly
success_percentage: Backend: 100% (12/12 tests passed), Frontend: 95% (1 minor UI issue)
